<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">Dear <%= @freelancer.name %>,</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Congratulations! You have successfully accepted the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" on GigHive.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;"><strong>Task Details:</strong></p>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Title:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Description:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Budget:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ", format: "%u%n") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Deadline:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Please coordinate with the client to ensure timely completion of the task. Meeting the deadline will contribute to building trust and strengthening your profile on GigHive.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  For more information or to manage the task, click the link below:
</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <%= link_to 'View Task on GigHive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;' %>
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  We wish you a successful and productive collaboration! Thank you for being a valued member of GigHive.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Sincerely,<br>
  The GigHive Team
</p>